## Pass Completion Gate Note


- `frontend-microinteraction-pass` delivered targeted high-density cluster mapping and durable cross-links.
- `frontend-long-tail-pass` now adds durable helper/shell coverage for sysadmin section scope, scoped registry launches, bulk mentor preview/apply, action-queue dismiss semantics, session restore/login gates, and the active faculty calendar modal planner, while also classifying `src/system-admin-timetable-editor.tsx` as a repo-present but currently unmounted alternate implementation.
- Remaining uncovered delta: telemetry/startup-diagnostics, `src/data.old.ts` formal archival decision, exhaustive every-component tail coverage for the rest of `src/`, backend active-run/helper services, parity seed lineage, live helper scripts, durable script-behavior mapping, durable same-student parity evidence, and authenticated behavior confirmation.
- Recommended next pass: rerun `script-behavior-pass` with durable outputs, then rerun `same-student-cross-surface-parity-pass` with explicit blocked/live evidence, with telemetry/startup mapping and a credentialed `live-behavior-pass` rerun still required afterward.

