===== audit-map/19-runbooks/live-vs-local-comparison-runbook.md =====
# Live vs Local Comparison Runbook

1. Run the same target flow locally and live.
2. Save both artifact sets separately.
3. Compare:
   - route reached
   - visible controls
   - API calls
   - error/loading states
   - role scope
4. Log mismatches in `10-live-behavior/live-vs-local-matrix.md` and `14-reconciliation/`.

