| Pages shell root | GitHub Pages should serve the current `air-mentor-ui` HTML shell with `/AirMentor/assets/...` references | Bootstrap headers show `200`, and both live-pass web fetches reached the same HTML shell; direct Node refresh in the native shell is still blocked by `getaddrinfo EBUSY` | Verified at HTML-shell level | `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T221302Z--pages-root--live--headers--bootstrap.txt`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T164511Z--pages-shell--live--web-observation--live-pass.md`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T174110Z--pages-shell--live--web-observation--live-pass.md` |
| Pages shell vs clean committed source | Clean committed `HEAD` Pages-style build should match the deployed shell if Pages is current | Clean committed build HTML is byte-identical to the bootstrap live HTML shell | Verified | `audit-map/17-artifacts/local/2026-04-15T164514Z--pages-root--local--html-shell--head-build.html`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/diffs/2026-04-15T164515Z--pages-root--diff--head-parity--live-pass.md` |
| Pages shell vs dirty worktree build | Dirty worktree output is not authoritative for deployment parity | Dirty-worktree Pages-style build emitted different `index` and `app-shared` hashes, but that difference disappeared when compared against a clean committed build | Resolved as local-only divergence | `audit-map/17-artifacts/diffs/2026-04-15T164515Z--pages-root--diff--head-parity--live-pass.md`, `audit-map/14-reconciliation/reconciliation-log.md` |
| Hash-route shell parity (`#/admin`) | Hash-only routes should still land on the same static shell | Both live-pass web fetches on `#/admin` returned the same shell as the root URL | Verified at shell level | `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T164511Z--pages-shell--live--web-observation--live-pass.md`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T174110Z--pages-shell--live--web-observation--live-pass.md` |
| Railway `/health` | Railway should expose `GET /health` and return `200` | Latest direct live artifact still shows `404` with `x-railway-fallback: true`; the rerun still could not refresh it because Node fetch failed with `getaddrinfo EBUSY` and the web fetcher did not materialize Railway rows | Contradiction open | `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T221301Z--railway-health--live--headers--bootstrap.txt`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T164513Z--live-capture-path--live--environment-blocker--live-pass.md`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T174110Z--live-capture-path--live--environment-blocker--live-pass.md` |
| Railway root and OpenAPI | Railway root should expose the status document and `/openapi.json` should expose the schema | No fresh response bodies were captured in either live-pass attempt because the current environment could not resolve or render Railway live responses | Environment blocked | `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T164513Z--live-capture-path--live--environment-blocker--live-pass.md`, `audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-15T174110Z--live-capture-path--live--environment-blocker--live-pass.md` |
