+# Live Credentialed Parity Report
+
+Pass: `live-credentialed-parity-pass`
+Context: `live`
+Date: `2026-04-16`
+Model/provider/account: `gpt-5.4 / native-codex / native-codex-session`
+Caveman used: `no`
+Live verification performed in this pass: `precondition-only`
+
