+**Outcome**
+
+The live-credentialed parity pass is now persisted as an explicit blocker, not a semantic parity proof. This run re-proved three current limits from fresh evidence: `verify:live-session-contract` fails immediately in this shell because `AIRMENTOR_LIVE_SYSTEM_ADMIN_IDENTIFIER` is unset, Playwright MCP still cancels before navigation, and the repo’s current proof/parity helpers are not safe for blind production use because they can mutate proof lifecycle or faculty records.
+
+I wrote the durable blocker artifacts to [live-same-student-parity.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/10-live-behavior/live-same-student-parity.md), [live-credentialed-parity-report.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/32-reports/live-credentialed-parity-report.md), [coverage-ledger.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/23-coverage/coverage-ledger.md), [review-status-by-path.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/23-coverage/review-status-by-path.md), [unreviewed-surface-list.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/23-coverage/unreviewed-surface-list.md), [contradiction-matrix.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/14-reconciliation/contradiction-matrix.md), [reconciliation-log.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/14-reconciliation/reconciliation-log.md), [working-knowledge.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/24-agent-memory/working-knowledge.md), [known-facts.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/24-agent-memory/known-facts.md), [known-ambiguities.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/24-agent-memory/known-ambiguities.md), [manual-action-required.md](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/25-accounts-routing/manual-action-required.md), the [status file](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/29-status/audit-air-mentor-ui-live-live-credentialed-parity-pass.status), and the paired [checkpoint](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/30-checkpoints/audit-air-mentor-ui-live-live-credentialed-parity-pass.checkpoint). New dated evidence is in [session-contract blocker](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-16T110353Z--live-session-contract--live--credential-blocker--parity-pass.txt), [Playwright MCP cancellation](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-16T110353Z--playwright-mcp--live--browser-cancelled--parity-pass.md), and [proof/parity safety audit](/home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/audit-map/17-artifacts/live/2026-04-16T110353Z--live-proof-parity-safety--code-audit--parity-pass.md).
+
+**Resume**
+
+Exact next command:
+```bash
+cd /home/raed/projects/air-mentor-ui/air-mentor-api && \
+RAILWAY_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api-production-ab72.up.railway.app \
+EXPECTED_FRONTEND_ORIGIN=https://raed2180416.github.io \
+AIRMENTOR_LIVE_SYSTEM_ADMIN_IDENTIFIER=<identifier> \
+AIRMENTOR_LIVE_SYSTEM_ADMIN_PASSWORD=<password> \
+npm run verify:live-session-contract
+```
+
+After that, do not run `playwright:admin-live:teaching-parity` on production until a read-only proof/parity observer exists or a full restore path is proven inside the same run. Current uncovered scope remains the shared live target tuple and same-target invariants across `SYSTEM_ADMIN`, `COURSE_LEADER`, `MENTOR`, `HOD`, and student-shell.
